data.message: We are sorry to announce the cancellation of the A-E 1969 Christmas Party on December 17, 2016 at Beck Cultural Exchange Center. We thank you for your responses and interest in our Event. From the A-E Class of 1969 we wish you a Merry Christmas & a Happy New Year...God Bless!

I hit select all for my friends list to invite to A-E Class of 1969 Party. It came up that I had reached my limit so I don't know who it stopped with but just in case please know that you are invited. That includes Loddy Doddy & Everybody...Love & Blessings!
What's the attire. Black Tie. 😜. We will be there.
